text: Park Kyong-nang (born ) is a South Korean female volleyball player. She was part of the South Korea women's national volleyball team at the 2005 FIVB World Grand Prix. On club level she played with Korea Tobacco & Ginseng. ==Clubs== * Korea Tobacco & Ginseng (2005) ==References== ==External links== *PIVB profile * FPV - Federação Paulista de Volleyball Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean women's volleyball players
